---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | Joner Football" description="Joner Football privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  <section class="min-h-screen bg-joner-black py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 font-body text-sm mb-12">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10">

        <!-- 1. Introduction -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed">
            Joner Football (operated by Lee Jones, ABN TBD) is committed to protecting your privacy under the Australian Privacy Principles (APPs). This policy explains how we collect, use, store, and disclose your personal information when you use our website (jonerfootball.com), the Joner Football App (app.jonerfootball.com), or any of our services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. Information We Collect -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mb-4">We may collect the following types of personal information:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-body">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Name and email address (via website forms, technique test, camp registrations)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Phone number (when provided in enquiry forms)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Usage data (cookies, page views, device information via Google Analytics 4)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Payment information (processed securely by Stripe and Uscreen, not stored by us)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- 3. How We Use Your Information -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mb-4">We use your personal information to:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-body">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Deliver training content and app services</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Send marketing emails (you can unsubscribe at any time)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Process payments for subscriptions, camps, and merchandise</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Improve our services and website experience</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Serve relevant advertising (Meta Pixel, Google Ads)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- 4. Cookies -->
        <div id="cookies" class="scroll-mt-32">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">4. Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We use cookies to improve your experience and understand how our website is used. Specifically:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-body">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Google Analytics 4 cookies for website analytics and traffic measurement</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Meta Pixel cookies for advertising measurement and retargeting</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mt-4">
            You can disable cookies in your browser settings. Please note that disabling cookies may affect your experience on our website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 5. Third-Party Services -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We use the following third-party services to operate our business. Each service has its own privacy policy:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-body">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Brevo (email marketing and contact management)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Stripe (payment processing)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Uscreen (app platform and subscription management)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> YouTube (video hosting and embedding)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Meta (Facebook and Instagram advertising)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Google (Analytics, Ads, and Search Console)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- 6. Data Retention -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">6. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed">
            We retain your email address and name until you request deletion or unsubscribe from our mailing list. Payment records are retained as required by Australian tax law. Analytics data is retained according to the default retention periods of Google Analytics 4 and Meta.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 7. Your Rights -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mb-4">Under the Australian Privacy Principles, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-body">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Request deletion of your personal information</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Unsubscribe from marketing communications at any time</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mt-4">
            To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:leejones@jonerfootball.com" class="text-joner-red hover:underline">leejones@jonerfootball.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 8. Contact -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">8. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mb-2">
            If you have any questions about this privacy policy, contact us:
          </p>
          <div class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed">
            <p>Joner Football</p>
            <p>20 Narabang Way, Belrose NSW 2085, Australia</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:leejones@jonerfootball.com" class="text-joner-red hover:underline">leejones@jonerfootball.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
